Fixes: 6a1e8d14156d4 ("crypto: talitos - making mapping helpers more generic")
Signed-off-by: Christophe Leroy <christophe.leroy@c-s.fr>
Signed-off-by: Herbert Xu <herbert@gondor.apana.org.au>
